OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Reg Charles
OL,5,FHe had known Major John Howard, who
OL,6,Fjust after midnight on 6 June led a
OL,7,Funit which captured two strategic
OL,8,Fbridges over the Orne river and canal
OL,9,Fahead of the beach landings.
OL,11,FIn doing so they secured a vital route
OL,12,Ffor the advancing Allies and became
OL,13,Fthe first troops to land and help
OL,14,Fliberate France.
OL,16,FThey are now known as the Pegasus and
OL,17,FHorsa bridges.
