OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Reg Charles
OL,5,FMr Charles said: "He (Major Howard)
OL,6,Fwas recruiting volunteers for crossing
OL,7,Fthe river and he asked me if I would
OL,8,Flike to join.
OL,10,F"It would mean going up in a glider
OL,11,Fand dropping down behind enemy lines.
OL,12,FI thanked him for the opportunity but
OL,13,Ftold him I would rather keep my feet
OL,14,Fon the ground."
OL,16,FMr Charles though did become part of
OL,17,FOperation Overlord and drove a Bren
OL,18,Fgun carrier.
