OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Reg Charles
OL,5,F"They decided as I could drive I could
OL,6,Fdrive a jeep. I drove a jeep on and
OL,7,Foff for the rest of the war."
OL,9,FMr Charles passed away a week after
OL,10,Fthis interview took place.
